sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: ADS Zone.Identifier Deleted By Uncommon Application
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects the deletion of the "Zone.Identifier" ADS by an uncommon process. Attackers can leverage this in order to bypass security restrictions that make use of the ADS such as Microsoft Office apps.

An adversary may attempt to get detailed information about the operating system and hardware, including version, patches, hotfixes, service packs, and architecture.
Adversaries may communicate using application layer protocols to avoid detection/network filtering by blending in with existing traffic.

Adversaries may abuse utilities that allow for command execution to bypass security restrictions that limit the use of command-line interpreters.

signature_matches.name: (internal) .NET file limitation
signature_matches.description:
internal/limitation/dynamic : This dynamic analysis trace describes a .NET file.

capa rules are not yet tuned for the .NET runtime, 
so its analysis may be incomplete or misleading.

rule:
  meta:
    name: (internal) .NET file limitation
    namespace: internal/limitation/dynamic
    authors:
      - "@v1bh475u"
    description: |
      This dynamic analysis trace describes a .NET file.

      capa rules are not yet tuned for the .NET runtime, 
      so its analysis may be incomplete or misleading.
    scopes:
      static: file
      dynamic: file
    examples:
      - 2f8a79b12a7a989ac7e5f6ec65050036588a92e65aeb6841e08dc228ff0e21b4_min_archive.zip

    - or:
      - format: dotnet
      - import: mscoree._CorExeMain
      - import: mscoree._corexemain
      - import: mscoree._CorDllMain
      - import: mscoree._cordllmain

signature_matches.name: get geographical location
signature_matches.description: collection
signature_matches.rule_src:
# generated using capa explorer for IDA Pro
rule:
  meta:
    name: get geographical location
    namespace: collection
    authors:
      - moritz.raabe
      - michael.hunhoff@mandiant.com
    scopes:
      static: function
      dynamic: call
    att&ck:
      - Discovery::System Location Discovery [T1614]
    examples:
      - 9879D201DC5ACA863F357184CD1F170E:0x10001A99
  features:
    - or:
      - api: GetLocaleInfo

      - api: kernel32.GetUserGeoID
      - api: kernel32.GetGeoInfo

      # "geo" and "zip" are too short
      # "region" results in FPs mostly related to memory
      - string: /geolocation/i
      - string: /geo-location/i
      - string: /^city/i
      - string: /region_code/i
      - string: /region_name/i
      - string: /^country/i
      - string: /country_code/i
      - string: /countrycode/i
      - string: /country_name/i
      - string: /continent_code/i
      - string: /continent_name/i
      - string: /^latitude/i
      - string: /^longitude/i
